<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.9.2">
<l>teruviltiri ciṟunōṉpiyar ceñcōṟṟoṭu kañci</l>
<l>maruvipirin tavarvāymoḻi matiyātuvan taṭaivīr</l>
<l>tiruvilpoli maṟaiyōrcciṟu puliyūrccala cayaṉat</l>
<l>turuvakkuṟa ḷaṭikaḷaṭi yuṇarmiṉṉuṇar vīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without [even] considering the utterances of those</l>
<l rend="indent">who are separate [from us], those who do [only] minimal fasting,</l>
<l>Who wander the streets, approaching [us] for fine rice and conjee,</l>
<l rend="indent">come [here] and take refuge;</l>
<l>You who would meditate, meditate on the feet of god, the beautiful dwarf</l>
<l>On the watery bed in Ciṟupuliyūr with Vedic experts who prosper in fortune.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
